## Pre-LLM Pipeline (run before every /architect or /ask)

Each ecosystem has its own pipeline. Run the one matching the project:

### Rust
```bash
cargo fmt && cargo clippy --fix --allow-dirty && cargo check
```

### Python
```bash
ruff format . && ruff check --fix . && mypy .
```

### PHP
```bash
php-cs-fixer fix && phpstan analyse --level=6
```

### JavaScript / TypeScript
```bash
prettier --write . && eslint --fix . && tsc --noEmit
```

> Rule: Run the pipeline first. The LLM only sees problems that tools cannot solve alone.

