## Testing Standards

| Layer          | Minimum coverage | Framework (by language)                     |
|----------------|-----------------|---------------------------------------------|
| Unit           | 90%             | cargo test / pytest / phpunit / vitest      |
| Integration    | Key paths       | cargo test --test / pytest / phpunit        |
| E2E (optional) | Happy path      | playwright (via mcp-playwright in stack)    |

- Write tests before implementation (TDD)
- Each test must have one clear assertion and a descriptive name
- Mocks allowed only at system boundaries (HTTP, DB, filesystem)

