## Architecture Memory Files

Every project using this stack must have these two files at its root:

**`ARCHITECTURE.md`** — records adopted technical decisions:
```markdown
# Architecture Decisions
## [Category]
- Decision: [what was decided]
- Reason: [why]
- Date: [YYYY-MM-DD]
```

**`CONSTRAINTS.md`** — records hard constraints:
```markdown
# Project Constraints
- [constraint] — [reason]
```

> Always `/add ARCHITECTURE.md CONSTRAINTS.md` at the start of each design session.
> Update after every significant architectural change.

